data.description: Don't miss out on this adorable 3BR/2BA home situated on a double lot spanning .3237 acres. It features a brand new 216 sf sunroom, as well as a large 20 x 23 2 car detached garage with its own private driveway. With vinyl siding, maintenance is a breeze. The majority of the home boasts tile flooring, while the bedrooms are carpeted. The family room, separate dining area, and well-equipped kitchen with ample cabinets, pantry, refrigerator, and electric stove provide plenty of space for everyday living. The split floor plan places the master bedroom, complete with a spacious walk-in closet and private ensuite bathroom, on one end. On the other side of the home, you'll find two bedrooms, a full bath, and a generously sized indoor laundry room. The backyard, which is fenced and boasts a firepit, offers endless possibilities. The roof, both on the house and detached garage, was replaced in October 2019. Hurricane shutters are conveniently stored in the garage. This move-in ready home awaits you.
